Welcome to Codam, a full-time programming course in the heart of Amsterdam!|1|
At Codam, you learn to program like a pro using our unique peer learning curriculum.|1|
We cover your tuition fees, there are no teachers and we are open 24/7!|1|
Moreover, Codam is accessible to everyone,|1|
because no previous education or diploma is required, to register you only have to be over 18.|1|
We believe that everyone can learn to program wherever you come from! #writeyourfuture|1|
